      <p>AU Small Finance Bank, based in the pink city Jaipur, is one of India's top-rated finance institutions. Known for supporting businesses with tailored loans, it also offers feature-rich credit cards that help you save while you spend. From cashback to reward points, AU credit cards are designed to give you more value every day.
</p>
      <h3>Who Can Apply?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Primary Cardholder: Age 21 to 60 years</li>
        <li>Add-on Cardholder: 18 years and above
</li>
<li>Eligibility: Resident of India
